text: Oddar Meanchey is a province of Cambodia. The capital is Samraong. It is in the Dângrêk Mountains. There are 4 districts and 1 municipality: *Anlong Veng *Banteay Ampil *Chong Kal *Samraong Municipality *Trapeang Prasat ==References== Category:Provinces of Cambodia Category:Establishments in Cambodia Category:1995 establishments in Asia Category:1964 establishments in Asia
title: Oddar Meanchey province
